extendedInfo.description: If bug exists, please tell us (E-mail), we will fix it as soon as possible.Dragon Age is a role-playing video game series created by BioWare. The first game, Dragon Age: Origins, was released in 2009. Dragon Age II, a sequel to Origins, was released in March 2011.In her courtesy of 53 wallpapers and icons.You can change the Wallpapers from the menu by selecting âChoose Wallpaperâ. The first five Wallpapers are stored in the application. Everyone else will be downloaded from the Internet and stored in a folder(wallpaper _duomob).This theme is compatible with Crazy Home Pro, Crazy Home Lite, ADW Launcher, Live Home, Open Home, Open Home 6, aHome, 91 Panda Home, 91 Panda Home 2.If using Crazy Home, once it is installed and running, press your Menu Key -> Crazy Menu -> Appearance -> Set Theme.If using ADW.Launcher, once it is installed and running, press your Menu Key -> More -> ADWSettings -> Themes Preferences.If using Go Launcher Ex, once it is installed and running, press your Menu Key -> Themes-> Select theme-> Apply.This application does not violate the copyright and does not claim to it.All that is in this appendix are collected from free sources.If you are the author of the material or the copyright holder for it and against its use in this, please contact me and the material will be removed or will be listed your copyright.

reviews.title: Love it!
reviews.comment: I get themes for icons only and these icons are amazing! I don\'t get the comment that states the icons are bad. Maybe that person needs glasses! These icons are detailed, 3D look & not cartoonish. Devs are getting stuck on making icons, themes, that look like they\'re for kids & this theme is just the opposite. I use the icons on Next Launcher by using manual apply or themes mix. Great job dev!
